Executive Summary
Former Army Captain Bergh took the reins of jean maker Levi Strauss & Co. in September 2011, replacing the retiring John Anderson, who stepped down after 32 years with the company. Bergh is a veteran consumer products executive, having spent the previous 28 years with Procter & Gamble. Bergh joined Levi Strauss & Co. at a t 
